OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThe Wire creator boycotts  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffilming new show in Texas  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fover abortion law          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, David Simon, who created the           
OL,6, Emmy-nominated US crime series The     
OL,7, Wire, has said he will not film his    
OL,8, forthcoming show in Texas, due to a new
OL,9, law there restricting access to        
OL,10, abortions.                             
OL,12,FThe new law bans abortion from as early
OL,13,Fas six weeks into pregnancy.           
OL,15,F"As an employer, this is beyond        
OL,16,Fpolitics," Simon posted on Twitter. "I 
OL,17,Fcan't and won't ask female cast/crew to
OL,18,Fforgo civil liberties to film there.   
OL,20,FHe also asked his followers to suggest 
OL,21,Falternative filming locations.         
